Frequently Asked Questions

How far in advance should I book?

We recommend booking at least 2-3 months in advance for corporate events and 1-2 months for private parties. Popular dates fill up quickly!

What's included in the booking fee?

The booking fee includes the performance, travel within Mumbai, and basic sound requirements. Additional services like accommodation or special equipment may incur extra costs.

Can Onkar perform in languages other than Hindi?

Yes! Onkar is comfortable performing in Hindi, English, and Marathi. He can also adapt his material to include regional humor when appropriate.

What if I need to cancel or reschedule?

We understand that plans can change. Cancellations made 30+ days in advance are fully refundable. Rescheduling is possible based on availability.
